# NSScroller.KnobStyle.dark

**Case**

Specifies a dark knob.

## Declaration

```swift
case dark
```

## Discussion

This style is particularly good against a light background.

## Constants

- **NSScroller.KnobStyle.default**: Specifies a dark knob with a light border.
- **NSScroller.KnobStyle.light**: Specifies a light knob.
